Earths psychologists have found the perfect solution to overpopulation. With an industrial strengh electric sander, and a hearty coat of paint, previously hostile environments can be brought to reign. Human beings cant tell the difference! (Mice cant, how different are we?)
 
 Our ride explores an astroid in the process of beautification (terafondling). Being pyschologists however, they missed the black hole in nearby proximity, which restrained its ruffian gravitational impulses in true predatory style, much to our entertainment delight. This footage was expelled from teh black hole in a further physical anomoly.

